::Squizzy::

The doors open in the room in which Vamprah's temporary bed was 
located and the lights turn on as Squizzy enters. She walks 
cheerfully to Vamprah. The femm should be feeling better by now.

"Rise and shine!" Squizzy says, putting down the tray of energon 
cubes she had carried into the room with her.
